00:00:33.742 --> 00:00:36.988
What are you going to cook for us today?
Kakara Pitha (Semolina Fritters)

00:00:47.663 --> 00:00:49.648
Ingredients required for Kakara Pitha

00:00:50.569 --> 00:00:55.119
Semolina, Raw coconut, Sugar &amp; Oil

00:01:08.824 --> 00:01:13.655
First roast some grated raw coconut in a pan

00:01:40.809 --> 00:01:57.541
Now add half cup of sugar, some water into the pan &amp; mix them well

00:02:09.779 --> 00:02:15.102
Now let it cook till the sugar melt and form into a paste

00:02:22.799 --> 00:02:25.654
Take the sugar paste mix into a bowl &amp; keep it aside

00:02:29.640 --> 00:02:40.035
Now boil two cups of water in the pan

00:02:42.819 --> 00:02:51.190
Add some sugar into the boiling water &amp;
mix them well until the sugar melts

00:03:00.705 --> 00:03:12.868
Add one cup of semolina into the pan &amp; mix it well

00:03:45.548 --> 00:03:53.144
Now heat some oil in a pan

00:03:53.144 --> 00:04:06.903
Now roll the cooked semolina into the shape of muffin cups

00:04:10.454 --> 00:04:16.243
Stuff the semolina cups with the prepared coconut mix

00:04:17.086 --> 00:04:19.369
Now press them into a round thin layer

00:04:21.759 --> 00:04:37.023
Deep fry the thin round shaped semolina until it turns brown in colour

00:04:40.408 --> 00:04:43.446
Take the Kakara Pitha into a serving plate

